PortSystem 1.0
PortGroup cmake 1.0

name                clog
version             1.3.0
categories          sysutils textproc
platforms           darwin
license             MIT
maintainers         raimue openmaintainer
description         A colorized log tail utility
long_description \
    Clog is a colorized log tail utility. It can spot patterns in an input \
    stream and colorize or suppress the lines. It can also decorate the lines \
    with time- or date-stamps.

homepage            https://tasktools.org/
master_sites        https://tasktools.org/download/

checksums           rmd160  b4044ebd891cd6ca88c314fd397782e57ab77a70 \
